        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York 43 Carmine Str.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>August 17th 5611</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee>!</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Since the receipt of your last favour I was very much<lb/> engaged
                with various objects &amp; was prevented from attending to our business;<lb/> This
                is the cause of my negligence &amp; therefore trust to be excused.â€”Now to<lb/> the
                Principal; Enclosed you will find 14 Dollars, One Doll &amp; 68<lb/> cents you will
                please to take for the 6 times insertion of my advertisement in your<lb/>
                <sic>Oxident</sic>, &amp; for the remainder you will oblige me by sending the
                following books</p>
            <table cols="4" rows="7">
                <row>
                    <cell>18</cell>
                    <cell><persName>Peixotto's</persName>
                        <add>?</add> at 4.50 per Dozn</cell>
                    <cell> - - -</cell>
                    <cell>6.75</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>24</cell>
                    <cell><persName>Nathan's</persName> Road to Faith</cell>
                    <cell>2 Do</cell>
                    <cell>4</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>24</cell>
                    <cell><persName>Pike's</persName> Torph. Questions</cell>
                    <cell>/95</cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">1.50</hi>
                    </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>12.25</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>1.63</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>â€”â€”â€”</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell/>
                    <cell>$13.88</cell>
                </row>
            </table>
            <p>I should have liked to introduce your learned<lb/>
                <sic>Catachism</sic> in my school but from the<lb/> youthfulness of my pupils &amp;
                incapability of comprehending it I am compelled<lb/> to defer using it until they
                have gone through the others. I am also sorry to<lb/> say that I am supplied with a
                great number of Hebrew spelling books which for the<lb/> present I must decline
                ordering any more Trusting that this will meet you in<lb/> good health. I remain Dr
                Sir your Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">ALoewe</persName>
            </p>
